2024-10-31T14:30:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Anya Taylor Joy wearing early American settler clothes, kneeling with her hands folded to pray in The Witch\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Photo: A24 via Everett Collection\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/06/MCDWITC_EC027.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap is-lead\">Whether it\u2019s something gory and macabre, silly and irreverent, or eerie and unsettling, the genre of horror is as rich and varied as the multitude of ghosts, ghoulies, and homicidal maniacs that go bump in the night.</p>\n\n<p>Looking for the best horror films available to stream on Netflix, <a href=\"https://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=nOD/rLJHOac&amp;offerid=852731.1321&amp;type=3&amp;u1=PolygonHorrorMovies092022\">Hulu</a>, <a href=\"https://hbomax.prf.hn/click/camref:1101lqHRA/pubref:PolygonHorrorMovies092022/%5Bp_id:11", "id": 1424283, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/22725152/best-horror-movies-netflix-amazon-prime-hulu-hbo", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The best horror movies you can watch right now", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-31T14:06:52+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"A jack-o\u2019-lantern with its face carved with spikey teeth, and eyes gouged onto its surface, to look like a Chain Chomp from Mario Bros. games.\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Photo: Petrana Radulovic/Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/IMG_5250.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=13,12.533333333333,71.6,70.133333333333\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">It\u2019s hard to know what to carve every year! Sure, you can just put some spooky eyes and teeth on your jack-o\u2019-lantern and call it a day, but this year we decided to be a bit more ambitious and organize a themed pumpkin carving session. The prompt? \u201cSpooky video game monsters.\u201d Did we succeed? Judge accordingly, and be sure to read the artist statements below each offering.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Can\u2019t get enough jack-o\u2019-lanterns? Travel back in time to our 2020", "id": 1423911, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/gaming/472884/jack-o-lantern-video-game-monsters", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Polygon\u2019s jack-o\u2019-lantern tributes to iconic gaming monsters", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-31T13:39:39+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"A screenshot shows the DSSA Callisto.\" data-caption=\"A view of the DSSA Callisto from inside the blue tube. | Image: Frontier Developments via Polygon\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Frontier Developments via Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/08/elite-dangerous-dssa-calisto-exit-jump-from-system-byeia-euq-qy-g-c24-1.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption>A view of the DSSA Callisto from inside the blue tube. | Image: Frontier Developments via Polygon</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">On December 15, multiplayer spacefaring game <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/guides/22301694/elite-dangerous-beginners-tips-tricks-getting-started-pc-xbox\">Elite Dangerous</a> </em>will enter its second decade of live service. The game, played inside a realistic recreation of all 400 billion star systems in our Milky Way galaxy, has change", "id": 1423912, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/pc/473158/elite-dangerous-colonization-expansion-bubble", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Elite Dangerous will let players colonize the Milky Way in 2025", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-31T13:10:51+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/xaMIvuorPgfCqjlhWPZ79qqn.webp?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Toby Fox has finally confirmed a release window for the next two chapters of <em>Deltarune</em>,<em> </em>roughly <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/2018/10/31/18048352/deltarune-undertale-toby-fox-story-gameplay\">six years after the game\u2019s initial release</a>. Chapter 3 and Chapter 4 will \u201c100% come out in 2025,\u201d <a href=\"https://x.com/tobyfox/status/1851836949847281963\">Fox said via X</a>. The <em>Undertale </em>creator shared the update on development progress with a Halloween illustration on Thursday.</p>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitt", "id": 1423419, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/gaming/473105/deltarune-chapter-3-4-release-date", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Toby Fox will release the next chapters of Deltarune in 2025", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-31T13:00:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Billy (Joe Locke) in close-up in a still from Agatha All Along\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Marvel Studios\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/FMM2000_106_8176_1038_R.jpeg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap has-text-align-none\">The second that <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/marvel/467165/agatha-all-along-mcu-analysis-villain\">Agatha All Along</a></em>\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/marvel/453241/who-is-teen-in-agatha-all-along\">\u201cTeen,\u201d aka Billy Kaplan</a> (Joe Locke), started spouting trivia about <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/marvel/455846/agatha-witch-magic-rules-how\">Agatha Harkness</a>, saying he was a big fan of her \u201cSalem era,\u201d I groaned. Not again. Even though part of that was an act with an ulterior motive, he\u2019s along for the ride in a way that feels so familiar a", "id": 1423420, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/opinion/472406/marvel-mcu-agatha-young-avengers-billy-wiccan-spiderman-sidekick", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Agatha All Along proves Marvel has a sidekick problem", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-31T12:28:10+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Activision\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/09/black-ops-4-xm4-loadout.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 </em>is Activision\u2019s biggest Call of Duty launch ever, Microsoft said during an earnings presentation on Wednesday. On the earnings call, Microsoft CEO Satya Nadella said <em>Black Ops 6</em> <a href=\"https://view.officeapps.live.com/op/view.aspx?src=https://microsoft.com/en-us/investor/earnings/FY-2025-Q1/Document/DownloadDocument/59/TranscriptQandAFY25q1.docx\">set a franchise record for release day players</a> and new Xbox Game Pass subscribers. Sales on PlayStation and Windows PC via Steam were up 60% over last year\u2019s sales numbers, he added. Microsoft did not mention how the game has sold on Xbox. Activisio", "id": 1423421, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/gaming/472964/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-biggest-call-of-duty-release-ever", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 has the biggest Call of Duty launch ever", "vote": 0}, {"age": nu